::Magmatron::

    In his communication room he set up for contacting Shredder. Soon he 
found his signal. He sent a secret transmission to him.
    "Shredder I don't know you really well, and you don't know me at all, but 
Bazooka says your a good fighter. I could use someone like you in my quest. 
My quest is to control all of Cyberton, and having you on my side would 
almost ensure my victory. If you decide to join me in my quest then ditch the 
other bots with you, whoever they may be and go to this signal, Bazooka will 
be waiting for you. Magmatron out."
    "Bazooka go to sector 324.56 and meet Shredder, If he decides to join us."
